member.name: T:Xamarin.Messaging.Diagnostics.UserTraceExtensions
member.summary: Provides additional tracing extensions for issuing user-visibile traces.
member.devdoc: The user-visible traces are always done prepending the "!" character to denote that it's a message for the user traces. The corresponding trace listeners (i.e. the one that outputs to the output window) will filter all traces and only output those that start with that character. This allows the components to freely trace both diagnostic-level messages in addition to user-visible ones, using the same API. The User* overloads will still trace to the normal traces (i.e. UserInfo does Info too). This also means that the system listeners need to filter out those messages with the given starting "!" character, to avoid duplicates.
